title: Tea with Mussolini (1999) Judi Dench + Cher (Optional Swesubs)
description:
Optional Swedish subtitles in separate idx/sub files. <a href="

Britain's great old ladies and Oscar-winners, Judi Dench and Maggie Smith in the same film, and together with Cher! This quality drama from Italy during WW2 portrays the charming and eccentric British ladies living there in their own word, almost refusing to accept that a war was goin on.

Written and directed by famous multitalent Franco Zeffirelli, based on his own childhood experiences.

DVDrip 2-pass, XviD
Widescreen 784x384, great stereo sound AC3.
Burn tested, runs well in both my standalone DivX players.
